div1.p:
Grimes call'd Edward White, who had known him six years; Mr Magennis, seven;
Mary Butcher
, four;
Sarah Starr
, Serjeant Salmon, nine or ten; Serjeant Macdaniel, ten or eleven; Serjeant Becket, nine; Serjeant Marshall, ten; who all gave him a good character.

Murray call'd
Daniel Sullivan
, who had known him six or seven years;
James Keyton
, five;
John Conner
, five or six;
William Young
, six or seven; and Mr Price, about ten; who all gave him a good character.
